title: Ciao Broth by INABA Wet Cat Food - Chicken with Scallop - 12 Packs (480g total) / Moist Treat, Delicious & Healthy Snack, Food Topper, Side Dish, Complement, Natural, Grain Free, Wet Cat Food
features: MADE WITH WHOLESOME INGREDIENTS YOU CAN TRUST: Every Inaba product is made with yummy, human-grade ingredients including farm-raised chicken and/or natural wild caught tuna
KEEP YOUR FELINE HYDRATED: Each delicious Inaba Chicken Broth Pouch contains 93% moisture, which is a great way to hydrate cats who naturally tend not to drink enough water

COMPLEMENT YOUR KITTY'S MEALS: Does your kitty come looking for more when their bowl is empty? Add a pouch of Inaba Broth as a side dish, use as a wet/dry cat food topper or give as a special treat without adding a lot of extra calories

SAVORY AND SUCCULENT: The first ingredient is chicken broth made from 100% natural farm-raised chicken, then Inaba mixes in succulent flakes of natural chicken, tuna, scallop or salmon- giving your fussy feline four fantastic flavours to choose
PERFECT PORTIONS: Kitties of all ages (kitten to senior) will slurp these savory broths. Perfect as an appetizer or to supplement feeding- use a whole pouch or refrigerate leftovers
description: From the manufacturer Here at Inaba, we know that your cat is a beloved member of your family. That's why our Grain-Free Chicken Broths start with 100% natural farm-raised chickens and contain no grains, preservatives or artificial colors. Each pouch contains a healthy serving of chicken broth mixed with succulent flakes of chicken, dolphin-safe tuna, scallop or salmon. With Vitamin E (an essential nutrient that helps support your cat's immune system), 93% moisture to help aid with feline hydration and 20 kcal per pouch, these are a healthy low calorie treat you can feel good about feeding your cat. Perfect for all ages- kitten to senior, simply tear open a pouch and pour out the delicious mix of gravy and flaky meat. Use as a side dish, a complement to a meal, a wet/dry cat food topper or as a special treat. Inaba makes snack time fun for you and your furry friends.
